{"tid":1944451,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"涉賣冒牌波鞋 警疑拒捕襲海關","createTime":"2020-03-26T11:33:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-26T17:06:28.000Z","uid":25558,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"f0255d3eb9783a48de8ca490a22b87ef4a1eb288","tid":1944451,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T11:33:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200326/RVBVPNDQ6I7HOGD7YE6OJXZ2LM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200326%2FRVBVPNDQ6I7HOGD7YE6OJXZ2LM%2F&d=NMuDHS38lj0XaiXuPCYWR3O0ZW31AiaZ%2BXmqixBX3cM%3D&h=7c275fb2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200326%2FRVBVPNDQ6I7HOGD7YE6OJXZ2LM%2F&h=1198e5cf\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200326/RVBVPNDQ6I7HOGD7YE6OJXZ2LM/</a><br />\n<br />\n涉賣冒牌波鞋 警疑拒捕襲海關<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200326/large/1585154268_6f74.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200326%2Flarge%2F1585154268_6f74.jpg&h=b2738c6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n被告警員黃港恆涉賣冒牌波鞋及拒捕，昨日應訊。何家達攝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】有年輕警員去年涉嫌於二手商品網站出售假波鞋，及後相約買家到觀塘港鐵站交收時，當場遭海關人員拘捕。警員更疑一度拒捕，令海關人員受傷。案件昨日提堂，涉案警員被控出售應用偽造商標貨品及抗拒海關人員等四罪，獲准保釋，案件5月25日再訊。<br />\n<br />\n散庭後變身<br />\n<br />\n被告黃港恆（25歲），報稱職業為警員。他被控出售冒牌貨，及為售賣或用作商業等用途而管有冒牌貨罪。控罪指他去年9月26日在觀塘港鐵站A出口大堂附近，出售一對有「adidas」字樣的波鞋，及管有兩對有「adidas」字樣的波鞋。他另被控於同日同地抗拒正在執行職務的海關人員鄭家健及馮展偉（俱為譯音）。<br />\n<br />\n辯方申請被告暫毋須答辯，案件押後八周以索取文件及尋求法律意見。被告續准以現金2,000元保釋。被告昨以一身斯文打扮應訊，聆訊後他到法院內的洗手間更衣，換上黑衫黑褲，並且戴上黑色鴨舌帽及太陽眼鏡離開法院大樓。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：WKCC691/20"},{"pid":"591a115aa5bb41e9c4647fa47b3c45693c774529","tid":1944451,"uid":206691,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T11:35:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a11b162906345ae2ce0b83864724cf9623b1656","tid":1944451,"uid":6845,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T11:35:55.000Z","msg":"換上黑衫黑褲，並且戴上黑色鴨舌帽及太陽眼鏡離開法院大樓。"},{"pid":"11b23a4b0d830125804785b09b549ba5f81a28b3","tid":1944451,"uid":187664,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T11:36:45.000Z","msg":"咁撚多OT錢都要靠呃人錢"},{"pid":"8a46f7fc0cec431f67f9effd235df7320b61fd50","tid":1944451,"uid":214502,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T11:39:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">警賊</span>"},{"pid":"e22dfa960fc44c816a2086964b675f68addbdc59","tid":1944451,"uid":16256,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4a11b162906345ae2ce0b83864724cf9623b1656","tid":1944451,"uid":6845,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T11:35:55.000Z","msg":"換上黑衫黑褲，並且戴上黑色鴨舌帽及太陽眼鏡離開法院大樓。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T11:39:31.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d716553440ac69b6af24de992aee97bb7531d44","tid":1944451,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T11:40:05.000Z","msg":"賊"},{"pid":"6dcdee735bf2d412f1cf5d45b992affaf17ded1e","tid":1944451,"uid":96648,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T11:45:42.000Z","msg":"休班狗不嬲係作奸犯科嘅代名詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0544f7de44afd96509b3b20b8a14096046e4c913","tid":1944451,"uid":54126,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T11:46:30.000Z","msg":"成班有牌賊仔"},{"pid":"441a9a3a5b13bb46ef26e674d54ad24061a23b30","tid":1944451,"uid":8014,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T11:47:07.000Z","msg":"抗拒正在執行職務的海關人員鄭家健及馮展偉<br />\n<br />\n呢2件肯定係yc 死曱甴老屈啊sir<br />\n我地savehk 藍營支持驚察 秘撈賣鞋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"